Hardware Timing Validator CLI

Usage: validate-timing [options]

Options:
  -d, --duration <ms>     Test duration in milliseconds (default: 3000)
  -f, --fps <fps>         Target frame rate for testing (default: 60)
  -o, --output <file>     Output file path for results
